BEST TRAINING COURSES One to One

Course in Beauty Therapy

ADVANCED COURSE
WITH LUCAS

Lucas gives you the platform to become a professional cosmetologist. Advanced Course in Cosmetology gives you a scope to learn from experts, practice under their guidance, and to get trained on the usage of industry-specific tools. All these are essential for establishing yourself as a professional beautician .

ELIGIBILITY CRITERIA :

You can join as soon as you complete your Class 10 (any stream).

GET HANDS-ON TRAINING IN

As part of the advanced course get complete guidance & practical training in

  • Grooming, Hygiene & Safety
  • Understanding skin type & Analysis
  • Cleansing & Toning practice
  • Exfoliation & Extraction
  • Massage Manipulation
  • Anti pigmentation treatment
  • Hands & Feet massage
  • Manicure & Pedicure
  • Hair Spa & Hair Treatments
  • Straightening
  • Perm
  • Keratin
  • Hair Art & Bridal Hair Styling
  • Basic Hair cuts
  • Grey Coverage and Root Touch ups
  • Blow drying and Heat styling
  • Treatments for Hair fall and Dandruff
  • Hair spas/ Hair Oil Massage
  • Creative Haircuts and Colouring
  • Men’s Hair Cuts
